message.raw:
* setup.py: add more warnings for C compilation

* genomedata/_load_seq.py: always makes chromosome and supercontig
  coordinates with unsigned 32-bit integers instead of system int

* genomedata/_query.py:

* src/genomedata_load_data.c: friendlier errors when invalid
  BED3+1/bedGraph data supplied; many changes to make variables more
  portable between 32-bit and 64-bit systems

* test/README: newfile
